    "Chats are End-to-end encrypted between your iPhone and Mac. The relay only sees ciphertext and connection metadata after the secure handshake completes." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你 iPhone 与 Mac 之间的聊天采用端到端加密。安全握手完成后，relay 只能看到密文和连接元数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Chats started in a project stay scoped to that working directory. If you pick No Project, the chat is global." : {
